high_descs: Take a left at the counter ahead, turn left at the fridge and walk to the wooden round table on the right.
Pick up the green sponge from the back right side of the table.
Turn right, take a right at the wall, turn left at the counter and walk to the white stove on the right.
Put the sponge inside the black pot on the back right corner of the stove.
Pick up the pot with the sponge from the stove.
Turn right, take a right at the counter, turn left at the fridge, and turn right at the wall to walk to the wooden round table on the right.
Put the pot with the sponge on the left side of the table in front of the bottle.
anns.task_desc: Place a pot with a sponge on a table.

high_descs: Go forward and to the right to stand at the round table.
Pick the green sponge up from the table.
Go right and cross the room to stand in front of the stove.
Put the sponge in the pot on the back, right burner of the stove.
Pick the pot up from the stove.
Go right and then right again and stand in front of the round table.
Put the pot down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a sponge in it on the table.

high_descs: Walk ahead to the counter, then turn right and go to the table.
Pick up the sponge on the table.
Turn around and veer left to the stove.
Place the sponge in the back right pot on the stove.
Pick up the pot.
Turn right and walk to the counter, then right again and walk back to the table.
Place the pot on the table to the left of the wine bottle.
anns.task_desc: Place a sponge in a pot on a table.
